  id: foxyJumpscare
  title: 1/10000 Chance for Foxy Jumpscare Every Second
  author: Moon
  description: "\"Like I said, he was always my favorite...\"\r\n\r\nEvery second
    of gameplay will roll a 1/10000 chance to play a random Foxy jumpscare from the
    Five Nights at Freddy's series. As if defusing bombs wasn't already scary enough.
    Mod settings are available to change the chance, seconds delay, and the available
    jumpscares. You can also enable it to jumpscare in the menus too if you're into
    that sort of thing. If there's any bugs, let me know on the Discord at Moon (poncley).\r\n\r\nCredit
    to Masked Mystery for the idea, Scott Cawthon for making the games, and YMY for
    making the original mod in tModLoader (https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3481943642)."
  version: 1.0.0
  outputFolder: build
  debugBuild: 1
  previewImage: {fileID: 2800000, guid: e162a1fe76f34a84e828ed9b5c96ff39, type: 3}
